      "text": "// capturedContextReq records the shape of one contextualized-endpoint request\n// so tests can assert routing, auto-chunk mode, and batch splitting.\ntype capturedContextReq struct {\n\tinputType  string\n\tautoChunk  bool\n\tgroupSizes []int\n}",
